Messages Coming From Local Controllers:

   NodeID
   StateCount *space* timestamp
   (int)Received Tuples Count
   .
   .
   (int)State Tuples Count
   .
   .
   (int)Sent Tuples Count
   .
   .

Now the Local Controller Waits for command:

    1. RESUME - next rule evaluation is done
    
    2. CHANGESTATE
       (int)Tuples to Delete Count
       .
       .
       (int)Tuples to Add Count
       .
       .
       
